{"title":"Linux安装使用阿里云镜像","date":"2019-10-31T12:15:52.688Z","link":"2019/10/31/Linux安装使用阿里云镜像","updated":"2019-08-06T04:48:38.539Z","content":"<h3 id=\"Linux安装使用阿里云镜像\">Linux安装使用阿里云镜像<a href=\"2019/10/31/Linux安装使用阿里云镜像#Linux安装使用阿里云镜像\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">wget -O /etc/yum.repos.d/CentOS-Base.repo http://mirrors.aliyun.com/repo/Centos-7.repo</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yum clean all</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yum makecache</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yum install -y git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n","prev":{"title":"V笔记","link":"2019/10/31/V笔记"},"next":{"title":"CentOS安装使用，远程连接MySql","link":"2019/10/31/CentOS安装使用，远程连接MySql"},"plink":"http://yoursite.com/2019/10/31/Linux安装使用阿里云镜像/"}